  "body_text": null,
  "page": null,
  "source": "[a \\.maximal.in./ X]\nStates:\nwhen:\n. a is \\set\n. X is \\set\nthat:\n. forAll: x is \\set\n  where:\n  . x \"in\" X\n  then:\n  . if:\n    . a \\:precedes:/ x\n    then:\n    . x = a\nDocumented:\n. called: \"maximal element\"\n. written: \"a? \\text{ is maximal in } X?\"\n. description: \"An element $a$ is maximal in $X$ when $a \\preceq x$ implies $x = a$ for all $x \\in X$; equivalently, $a$ strictly precedes no element.\"\nId: \"47cae71f-185e-431a-bd38-a3ab7d08d070\"",
